Title: Frame-Up
Plot: Tony is accused of murdering a woman whos body was found at Quantico and the team must prove his innocence. All the possible evidence prove that Tony is guilty and the team will give their best to set their agent and a friend free.

GuestStars: Don Franklin, Michael Bellisario, Matt Malloy, Brian Dietzen, Lindsay Price, Elizabeth Ann Bennett, Jarrod Crawford, Randy Wayne, Joe Spano
